    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/ee959ede80406895aca03cf27cb9bdb9.avif?t=1748282919\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br>残酷，血腥，硬汉，毫不拖泥带水的动作。经典闯关题材的一次真正的复活。用最扭曲的手段杀死敌人，研究对手的行为，练习技巧并与你的伙伴在合作模式下杀出一条血路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/0dfd5a43ace91e5fc009eeb5bfc7010a.poster.avif?t=1748282919\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/0dfd5a43ace91e5fc009eeb5bfc7010a.webm?t=1748282919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/0dfd5a43ace91e5fc009eeb5bfc7010a.mp4?t=1748282919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这位残暴的俄罗斯人瓦西里是世界上最庞大武器商的前任安全执行官。 他在上级命令下敲诈、威胁、酷刑甚至残杀别人。 但是当瓦西里•决定离开这个肮脏的事业并东逃到一座孤立的修道院时，他变成了一名通缉犯。 嗯，这些人在自找麻烦……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/76484930cf002b3a070dd52cdc5358b3.avif?t=1748282919\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>激烈的俯视角操作：</strong> 使用各式各样的枪械和近战武器，例如格斗匕首，警棍，火焰斧，锤子来打倒敌人。<br></li><li><strong>拳拳到肉的暴力格斗：</strong> 以牙还牙，使用雇佣兵的残酷格斗技巧，连击，蓄力和跳跃攻击击败你的对手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/1b8b86f735e5da454dfa331549b00688.poster.avif?t=1748282919\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/1b8b86f735e5da454dfa331549b00688.webm?t=1748282919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/1b8b86f735e5da454dfa331549b00688.mp4?t=1748282919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>独特的杀敌系统：</strong>使用三种不同方式来无情地消灭敌人：无影无踪地执行优雅的潜行暗杀；发挥你的创造力，利用四周环境来杀死对手，砸烂他们的头骨，将他们摧毁并置于火焰中燃烧；或者你也可以选择直接刚正面，通过你娴熟的战斗技巧击败对手，残酷地处决敌人，成为全场最佳，触发击杀回放吧。<br></li><li><strong>闪避系统：</strong>防守，同时利用适当的时机击倒敌人。学习不同类型敌人的动作和攻击模式，强化你的挡反技巧，来一把吴克割草无双。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/86f88077b44545d02b38af1891f777eb.poster.avif?t=1748282919\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/86f88077b44545d02b38af1891f777eb.webm?t=1748282919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/86f88077b44545d02b38af1891f777eb.mp4?t=1748282919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>[*[b]]缴械和肢解系统：</li></ul>[/b]使用独特的手段来解除敌人的武装，或肢解特定敌人，并拿他们的四肢（头盖骨）当棒槌（碗）使。<br><li><strong>单人剧情战役：</strong>探索瓦西里的悲惨过去，体验这位武僧的背叛和救赎之旅。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/223b52c83dd96fd9e201a5bf6bf412aa.poster.avif?t=1748282919\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/223b52c83dd96fd9e201a5bf6bf412aa.webm?t=1748282919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/447290/extras/223b52c83dd96fd9e201a5bf6bf412aa.mp4?t=1748282919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>合作游戏。</strong>与朋友一起完成游戏，祝你的手柄能成为惩罚敌人的终极武器！<br></li><li><strong>竞技场模式：</strong>通过在竞技场模式中对抗无尽的敌人来练习并测试你的战斗技巧。<br></li><li><strong>角色职业规划：</strong>取决于你的偏好，将瓦西里打造成武僧或是士兵。</li>[/list]<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.